OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FQatar's energy minister has said its
OL,7,Fliquefied natural gas (LNG) export
OL,8,Fcapacity has been significantly
OL,9,Freduced following Iranian missile
OL,10,Fstrikes on facilities, as the Middle
OL,11,FEast war continues to send stock
OL,12,Fprices plummeting.
OL,14,FThe damage to Ras Laffan Industrial
OL,15,FCity, Qatar's main site for production
OL,16,Fof liquefied natural gas and gas-to-
OL,17,Fliquid, will take up to five years to
OL,18,Frecover, which will cause an expected
OL,19,Floss of $20 billion (#15 billion) in
OL,20,Fannual revenue, Saad Sherida Al-Kaabi
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
