FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774123872
OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,F"This was an attack on all of us who
OL,7,Fstand for development and human
OL,8,Fprogress that is sustained by a fair,
OL,9,Freliable, and secure access to
OL,10,Fenergy," Sherida Al-Kaabi said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,FIt comes as Iran launched further
OL,14,Fattacks on neighbouring countries
OL,15,Fovernight, with Kuwait and Saudi
OL,16,FArabia intercepting fire and shrapnel
OL,17,Fstriking a warehouse in Bahrain, as
OL,18,Fmany people observed Eid al-Fitr, the
OL,19,Fend of Ramadan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
