OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FIsrael hit the Iranian capital of
OL,7,FTehran on Friday morning, as Iranians
OL,8,Fmarked Nowruz, the Persian New Year.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
