OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FIsrael's Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu pledged on Thursday to
OL,8,Frefrain from further strikes on a key
OL,9,FIranian gas field at US President
OL,10,FDonald Trump's request, as attacks
OL,11,Fsent the price of brent crude oil up
OL,12,Fby 7% to reach $114 - around #86 - a
OL,13,Fbarrel.
OL,15,FBefore the war started, oil prices had
OL,16,Fnot passed the $100 per barrel mark
OL,17,Fsince July 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
