OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FIran's death toll now stands at 3,100
OL,7,Fpeople, HRANA said, while more than
OL,8,F1,000 people have died in Lebanon, and
OL,9,F15 in Israel. Thirteen US service
OL,10,Fmembers have been killed.
OL,12,FUK Prime Minister Keir Starmer said on
OL,13,FFriday he recognised the "pressure
OL,14,Frising costs puts on families" amid
OL,15,Fthe "uncertainty" of the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
