OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FStarmer has said that the "best way
OL,7,Fforward is a negotiated settlement
OL,8,Fwith Iran" amid the closure of the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz - a critical shipping
OL,10,Froute for oil and gas on which Iran
OL,11,Fhas effectively placed a blockade.
OL,13,FTehran has said it is only blocking
OL,14,Foff passage through the strait to
OL,15,FIran's "enemies".
OL,17,FQatar's LNG export capacity reduced
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
