OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FRas Laffan Industrial City was struck
OL,7,Fby Iran overnight into Thursday, with
OL,8,Fthe attacks damaging two of the site's
OL,9,F14 trains - the term for large
OL,10,Findustrial processing units.
OL,12,FThe units produce 12.8 million tons
OL,13,Fper annum, representing 17% of Qatar's
OL,14,Fexports, the energy minister said,
OL,15,Fwith the damage expected to take
OL,16,Fbetween three to five years to repair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
