OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774123872
OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,F"The impact is on China, South Korea,
OL,7,FItaly and Belgium. This means that we
OL,8,Fwill be compelled to declare force
OL,9,Fmajeure for up to five years on some
OL,10,Flong-term LNG contracts," Sherida Al-
OL,11,FKaabi said.
OL,13,FThe attacks also targeted the Pearl
OL,14,FGTL (gas-to-liquids) facility, that
OL,15,Fconverts natural gas into high-quality
OL,16,Fcleaner burning drop-in fuels and
OL,17,Fproduces base oils used to make
OL,18,Fpremium engine oils and lubricants,
OL,19,Fand paraffins and waxes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
