OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FThe damage caused to one of the two
OL,7,Ftrains at Pearl GTL is being assessed
OL,8,Fand is expected to be offline for a
OL,9,Fminimum of one year, Sherida Al-Kaabi
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FGulf states under fire during Eid
OL,14,FHeavy explosions shook Dubai in the
OL,15,FUnited Arab Emirates early Friday as
OL,16,Fair defenses intercepted incoming fire
OL,17,Fover the city.
OL,19,FThe Dubai Media Office, the
OL,20,Fsheikhdom's government communication's
OL,21,Farm, said no one was injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
