OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FKuwait reported two waves of drone
OL,7,Fstrikes at its Mina Al-Ahmadi oil
OL,8,Frefinery, one of three in the country,
OL,9,Fwhich sparked a fire at several of its
OL,10,Funits.
OL,12,FThe refinery, which can process some
OL,13,F730,000 barrels of oil per day, was
OL,14,Falready damaged on Thursday in another
OL,15,FIranian attack.
OL,17,FBahrain's Interior Ministry also
OL,18,Freported a fire erupting on Friday
OL,19,Fmorning after shrapnel fell on a
OL,20,Fwarehouse in the island kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
