OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FSaudi Arabia said it had shot down
OL,7,Fmultiple Iranian drones targeting its
OL,8,Foil-rich Eastern Province.
OL,10,FUnited Nations Security Council held
OL,11,Fan urgent closed meeting on Thursday,
OL,12,Fduring which Gulf countries stressed
OL,13,Fthe need for Iran to halt attacks on
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FNetanyahu vows not to attack natural
OL,17,Fgas field
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
