OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FIsrael will hold off on any further
OL,7,Fattacks on Iran's giant natural gas
OL,8,Ffield, at Trump's request, Netanyahu
OL,9,Fsaid during a televised address late
OL,10,Fon Thursday.
OL,12,FNetanyahu also denied that Israel had
OL,13,Fpressured the United States into going
OL,14,Fto war, amid growing US domestic
OL,15,Fconcerns about the country's
OL,16,Finvolvement.
OL,18,F"This canard that we dragged the
OL,19,FUnited States into this is not just a
OL,20,Fcanard, it's ridiculous," the prime
OL,21,Fminister said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774123872
OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,F"I didn't have to convince President
OL,7,FTrump about the need to prevent Iran
OL,8,Ffrom developing its nuclear programme,
OL,9,Fputting it underground, and being able
OL,10,Fto launch nuclear-tipped missiles at
OL,11,Fthe United States. He understood that."
OL,13,F"The world owes a debt of deep
OL,14,Findebtedness to President Trump for
OL,15,Fleading this effort to safeguard our
OL,16,Ffuture", he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
