OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FNetanyahu also claimed Iran now has
OL,7,F"no ability to enrich uranium at the
OL,8,Fmoment and no capability of
OL,9,Fmanufacturing ballistic missiles" due
OL,10,Fto the conflict.
OL,12,FIran's Revolutionary Guard
OL,13,Fspokesperson killed after saying
OL,14,Fmissiles still being made
OL,16,FThe spokesperson for Iran's
OL,17,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard has
OL,18,Fbeen killed in an airstrike, with his
OL,19,Fdeath announced shortly after he told
OL,20,Fa state-run newspaper that the war was
OL,21,Fnot yet over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
