OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FGen. Ali Mohammad Naeini also told the
OL,7,FIRAN newspaper Tehran is still
OL,8,Fbuilding missiles, despite Israel and
OL,9,Fthe US both stating that the country's
OL,10,Fweapons stock is depleting.
OL,12,F"There is no concern in this regard
OL,13,Fbecause we are producing missiles even
OL,14,Fduring war conditions, which is
OL,15,Famazing, and there is no particular
OL,16,Fproblem in stockpiling," Naeini said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
