OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774123872
OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,F"These people expect the war to
OL,7,Fcontinue until the enemy is completely
OL,8,Fexhausted. This war must end when the
OL,9,Fshadow of war is lifted from the
OL,10,Fcountry," he continued.
OL,12,FNaeini's death was announced by
OL,13,FIranian state television.
OL,15,FEU leaders demand Strait of Hormuz
OL,16,Freopens
