OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,FThe leaders of the 27 European Union
OL,7,Fcountries, known collectively as the
OL,8,FEuropean Council, have issued a joint
OL,9,Fstatement expressing their concern
OL,10,Fover the energy crisis and calling for
OL,11,F"de-escalation and maximum restraint"
OL,12,Ffrom all sides.
OL,14,FThey also demanded "freedom of
OL,15,Fnavigation in the Strait of Hormuz",
OL,16,Fasked Iran to stop striking
OL,17,Fneighbouring countries and sought
OL,18,Finternational cooperation to prevent a
OL,19,Flarge-scale refugee crises in the
OL,20,FMiddle East.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774123872
OL,3,CIranian attack on gas plant could take
OL,4,Cfive years to recover from, Qatar warns
OL,6,F"The European Council deplores the
OL,7,Floss of civilian life and is closely
OL,8,Fmonitoring the far-reaching impact of
OL,9,Fthe hostilities, including on economic
OL,10,Fstability," the statement, published
OL,11,Flate on Thursday, said.
OL,13,FAhead of the European Council meeting,
OL,14,FBelgian Prime Minister Bart De Wever
OL,15,Fsaid the EU countries are "very
OL,16,Fworried about the energy crisis",
OL,17,Fnoting that prices were already high
OL,18,Fbefore the war began.
OL,20,F"If that becomes structural, we're in
OL,21,Fdeep trouble," De Wever said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
